seasons.title: Alistair MacLean’s Air Force One is Down

episodes.synopsis: A general stages an elaborate plot to kidnap the U.S. president and deliver her to a Serbian strongman, by crashing Air Force One.
episodes.title: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: A renegade soldier accompanied by a crack team of experts must rescue the U.S. president and stop an attack on their home soil.
episodes.title: Part 2

video.title: Alistair MacLean’s Air Force One Is Down
video.synopsis: When a sabotaged Air Force One crash-lands in the Mediterranean, the first female U.S. president is taken captive by a Serbian strongman.
